Package org.GameObjects

Class ImmovableObject

java.lang.Object
org.GameObjects.ImmovableObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
BonusReward, Punishment, RegularReward
public abstract class ImmovableObject extends Object
Abstract class representing any object on the screen that is static, including carrots, mystical ocean fruits, and lava tiles.
